#: {{usex|You’d better watch it, '''friend'''.|lang=en}}
# {{context|computing|programming|lang=en}} In [[object-oriented programming]], a [[function]] or [[class]] granted special access to the [[private]] and [[protected]] [[member]]s of another class.
